Suggests: mesa-vulkan-drivers | libvulkan1
Description: World of Warships tools suite
 wows-toolkit is a Swiss army knife for World of Warships, providing:
  - wows_toolkit: GUI application for browsing replays, extracting game
    files, and previewing ship armor models (requires Vulkan/OpenGL 3.3+)
  - wowsunpack: command-line tool for unpacking IDX/PKG game asset archives
  - replayshark: command-line tool for analysing replay files
 .
 Note: Build requires Rust 1.92 or later. Debian's rustc package may be
 too old; install a recent toolchain via rustup if needed.
